  <brief_title>Comparison Between Pre and Intraoperative ERCP in Treatment of Common Bile Duct Stones</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Versus Intraoperative Endoscopic Sphincterotomy for Management of Choledocholithiasis and Cholecystolithiasis</official_title>
