  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      ERCP plays an important role in management of common bile duct stones. Herein the
      investigators compare preoperative against intraoperative ERCP.

      210 were included but only 198 patients were randomly divided into two groups; PES/LC (100
      patients) and LC/IOES (98 patients).

      The total hospital stay were significantly shorter in the group of LC/IOES
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
